eu.shooktea.vmsm.vmtype

Class VMType

  • java.lang.Object
    • eu.shooktea.vmsm.vmtype.VMType
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Vagrant

    public abstract class VMType
extends java.lang.Object
    Representation of type of virtual machine. While every virtual machine can have multiple modules, it will always have one and only one type. That type is set when creating new virtual machine in VMSM and cannot be changed.
